msgid ""
"To manage relations between tables, you can use the \"External ID\" "
"facilities of Odoo. The \"External ID\" of a record is the unique identifier"
" of this record in another application. This \"External ID\" must be unique "
"across all the records of all objects, so it's a good practice to prefix "
"this \"External ID\" with the name of the application or table. (like "
"'company_1', 'person_1' instead of '1')"
msgstr ""
"若要管理表格之間的關係，可以使用 Odoo 的「外部 ID」功能。記錄的「外部 ID」是該記錄在另一個應用程式中的唯一識別碼。此「外部 "
"ID」在所有物件的所有記錄中，都必須是唯一的，因此最好在此「外部 "
"ID」前面，加上應用程式或資料表的名稱作為字首（例如：company_1、person_1 而不是 \"1\"）"

